name: Zip, Zip, Zip
writer: Carter Bays (created by), Craig Thomas (created by), Brenda Hsueh, Kourtney Kang (executive story editor)

plot: Ted and Victoria had decided to wait for one month before sleeping together, but Victoria forgets that she'll be out of town on that day. Meanwhile Marshall and Lily celebrate their nine year anniversary, and Barney and Robin have a bros night out.
